title: Saturday Night Live Season 8 Complete
description:
SNL Season 8 (1982-1983)

The Eighth Season Of Saturday Night Live Went Ahead And Did What The Cast The Guests Hosts And The Musical Guests Did. It Became The Good Season Of Our Time.

Wherever Is Eddie Murphy Playing As Gumby Or Stevie Wonder.

And

Joe Piscopo Playing As Frank Sinatra Sr. 

SATURDAY NIGHT LIVE 8TH SEASON. BECAME THE TOP OF THE CHARTS OF TV'S LATE NIGHT. AS SO AS FOR DICK EBERSOL.

NOTE:DON PARDO ALSO RETURNED AS THE ANNOUNCER IN THIS SEASON.

AND ALSO DURING THE FIRST FEW SHOWS OF THE 8th SEASON. NBC WANTED TO GET RID OF ANDY KAUFMAN. BECAUSE HE WASN'T THAT TOO FUNNY. SO BY THE 7th SHOW OF THE 8th SEASON CAME AROUND. THEY DECIDED TO VOTE ANDY KAUFMAN OFF THE SHOW.
